snippet.title: Happi Basudei - PlayStation 4 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Oldschool platformer which you found on a random untitled cartridge. In this game, you can win by doing nothing! Well… Except evading.

Developed and published by Xeneder Team
Also released on PlayStation 5 and Xbox One

#ps4 #playstation4 #xenederteam #happibasudei #theforeseenarcade
